  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Take your<strong> chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Pat your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> dry with kitchen paper and season generously with<strong> salt </strong>and your <strong>ras el hanout</strong></p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over medium-high heat, then once hot, add the <strong>seasoned chicken</strong>, skin-side down, and cook for 10 min or until the skins have browned and crisped</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1715956988366-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1715956988366-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1715956988366-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1715956988366-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1715956988366-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> crispy chicken </strong>to a baking tray (skin side up), reserve the pan</p><p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips, then peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1715956991325-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
