    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>onion</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> <strong>strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until softened</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[680ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
