    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> with your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>giant</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> and the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, stirring occasionally, for 12-14 min or until all the water has absorbed and the giant couscous is tender</p>",
