    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, add your<strong> tahini </strong>to a small bowl<strong> </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>warm water </strong>and mix until fully combined and smooth</p><p>Add your<strong> natural yoghurt </strong>with<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then stir it all together – this is your <strong>tahini yoghurt</strong></p><p>Roll your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
