    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the giant couscous is tender, add your <strong>diced</strong> <strong>apricots</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
