      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy ras el hanout chicken </strong>over the <strong>giant couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>tahini</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong>, season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Tip: Drizzle over all the juices and caramelised bits from the chicken tray!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
